1313
01:12:53,896 --> 01:12:55,419
[Ledger sighs]

1314
01:12:55,463 --> 01:12:56,855
♪ On your side ♪

1315
01:12:56,899 --> 01:12:58,683
♪ Long blue light ♪

1316
